Detailed Description

template<typename KEY, typename VALUE, typename LOCK, typename ALLOCATOR>
class cds::ordered_list::details::lazy_list::Node< gc::no_gc, KEY, VALUE, LOCK, ALLOCATOR >

Lazy list node for implementation without node deletion (no reclamation schema needed)

Template parameters:

  • GC Memory reclamation schema
  • KEY type of key stored in list
  • VALUE type of value stored in list
  • LOCK lock primitive
